LOVE IS...
love is happy,
love is kind,
love is special,
in my mind,
love is lying,
love is cheat,
its an army of feelings,
you cannot defeat,
love is chocolate,
hugs and kisses,
red hearts and ribbons,
gallons of wishes,
love is bad news,
love is despair,
one moment love is in your heart,
the next its not there,
love is feelings,
love is stars,
love is shared,
love is ours,
love is running through fields,
love is climbing a tree,
i know what love is,
love is you and me.

